[He suddenly appears out of nowhere to help little kids, it's Miracle Ace]

4
00:00:07,150 --> 00:00:09,800
[Right now, Masao-kun is in trouble!]

5
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:12,400
[Please come and help! Masked Miracle Ace]

6
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:14,300
Stop it! Let me go!

7
00:00:15,370 --> 00:00:16,450
Stop!

8
00:00:18,170 --> 00:00:19,900
Miracle Ace!

9
00:00:29,270 --> 00:00:30,400
That was close, huh?

10
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:32,300
Thank you!
Yes

11
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:34,300
What is your name?

12
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,800
I'm Misao

13
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:36,550
Masao?

14
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:37,000
Yes

15
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,220
How do you write it?

16
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:41,650
Like this...

17
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:52,770
Mister, you're strong!

18
00:00:52,770 --> 00:00:54,820
Not really

19
00:00:55,870 --> 00:00:57,900
Mister, you have a lot of equipment, huh

20
00:00:58,020 --> 00:00:58,900
Yea

21
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,470
What is this?

22
00:01:00,970 --> 00:01:03,270
It's not anything special

23
00:01:03,270 --> 00:01:04,900
It's my cigarette case

24
00:01:08,850 --> 00:01:10,100
Tiring...

25
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:12,220
It's done

26
00:01:16,620 --> 00:01:18,870
Mister, you look really strong to me!

27
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:19,720
Really?

28
00:01:20,050 --> 00:01:21,970
Mister, is your whole family strong?

29
00:01:22,950 --> 00:01:24,950
My dad... isn't strong

30
00:01:24,950 --> 00:01:28,150
Well, my dad is retired

31
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,450
My older brother is also weak

32
00:01:33,650 --> 00:01:34,270
Really?

33
00:01:34,620 --> 00:01:36,220
Hmmm, my older brother...

34
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:37,770
well...

35
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:39,770
he was into track and running

36
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,750
My brother works at the credit union

37
00:01:43,850 --> 00:01:44,600
What?

38
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,670
Toyonaka shinyokinko (Toyonaka Credit Union)

39
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:50,070
He works there?

40
00:01:49,470 --> 00:01:50,060
Yes

41
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,850
Mister, don't you do any sports?

42
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:55,470
Not, not really

43
00:01:56,570 --> 00:01:59,100
Mister, I have a favor to ask

44
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:02,070
When I get bullied...

45
00:02:02,570 --> 00:02:03,920
next time something happens

46
00:02:04,170 --> 00:02:05,100
can you come?

47
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,100
If I'm off that day, I won't come

48
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,900
I work as a waiter in a coffee shop

49
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:16,350
So if I go there, I can see you?

50
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:18,220
Yes, well...

51
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,570
Mon, Wed, Fridays I work the early shift

52
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,620
Friday I work all day

53
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,620
Can you give me directions?

54
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:28,920
Yes, I'll write it down for you later

55
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:30,070
Really?
Yes

56
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,500
Ok... p..please
Yes

57
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:34,100
Definitely help me
Sure, no problem

58
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,370
Mister, what star did you come from?

59
00:02:36,370 --> 00:02:37,370
I can't tell you that

60
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:39,470
I can't say

61
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,000
So it's Miracle Ace!

62
00:02:49,550 --> 00:02:51,000
He has a lot of secrets!

